channel.title: What folders do i go into on my client for dragon claws?
channel.description:
I have been wanting to add dragon claws onto my server. I also knew that it is client sided, can anyone just tell me what file i open inside my client to add dragon claws I know how to do it i just need the folder.
Thank you all!

item.title: What folders do i go into on my client for dragon claws?
item.dc:creator: @_Ryan3 _Ryan
item.description:
@_Ryan3 wrote:

Add your Gzipped model into your models folder.

Add your correct ints (Which really dont matter unless you want to see them correctly)

Save compile

Open your client

type something like this

add model yourgzippedmodelid

close

Reopen done.
